## Expected Breakthrough Impact

Once the infinite loop issue is resolved, this system will enable:

1. **Living Code Archives**: Each image literally contains and executes source code
2. **Visual Programming History**: 99 languages preserved as functional art
3. **Educational Tools**: Students can see code execution in visual form
